sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant FE as Frontend (app.js)
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant RAG as RAG Chain
    participant RET as Retrieval
    participant RR as Reranker
    participant LLM as LLM / Fallback
    participant VS as Chroma Vector Store

    U->>FE: Type question
    FE->>API: POST /chat/stream {input, history}
    API->>RAG: rewrite + classify
    RAG->>RET: hybrid retrieve (BM25 + MMR)
    RET->>VS: query (k, fetch_k)
    VS-->>RET: candidate chunks
    RAG->>RR: rerank (optional)
    RR-->>RAG: reranked docs + scores
    RAG->>LLM: prompt(context, question)
    LLM-->>API: token stream
    API-->>FE: SSE events {type:'token', data}
    Note over API,FE: After stream completes
    FE->>API: POST /chat/invoke {input, history}
    API->>RAG: finalize answer + sources + confidence
    RAG-->>API: structured payload
    API-->>FE: JSON {answer, sources, rewritten_query, confidence}
    FE->>FE: Render markdown, footnotes, previews, feedback

    alt Low confidence or insufficient sources
        API->>FE: Clarify/ask follow‑up (hallucination guard)
    end
